item.title: CVE-2020-2111|2024-08-04T07:01:39.673Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20subversion%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Subversion Plugin 2.13.0 and earlier does not escape the error message for the Project Repository Base URL field form validation, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2020-2304|2024-08-04T07:09:53.361Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20subversion%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Subversion Plugin 2.13.1 and earlier does not configure its XML parser to prevent XML external entity (XXE) attacks.
